NAME
	si - short inventory

SYNOPSIS
	si [here/name/item]

DESCRIPTION
	A helpful command with places and containers which contain lots of
	stuff. "si here" gives the inventory of your location.

EXAMPLE
	> si
	Someone is carrying: Lord's crown (worn), Enhanced feelings,
	Enormous three-handed sword (wielded), Graah's staff of power and
	Thieve's tattoo.

SEE ALSO
	inventory
